{"tid":2166360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公投決定主權","createTime":"2020-08-20T11:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T11:37:14.000Z","uid":277640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"befd1ddb2901baa9174c5f6d6717c5a456623bc9","tid":2166360,"uid":277640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T11:21:33.000Z","msg":"睇完今集果籽之後，你諗吓自己，再諗吓直布羅陀呢個地方<br />\n<br />\n佢屬於英國海外領土，<span class=\"red\"><strong>可以自動攞到英國身分</strong></span>，有投票權。<br />\n<br />\n一個只有3.9萬人，<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">大過油尖旺小小</span></span>嘅地方，因為佢個戰略地位，個個想爭奪呢個地方。西班牙更一直聲稱有直布羅陀主權，想同英國共擁直布羅陀主權。1967年公投，99%想留英，兩年後訂立憲法，<span class=\"red\">英國唔可以決定佢嘅主權</span>，2002年有98%唔同意俾西班牙共擁主權。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">直布羅陀喺憲法下擁有高度自治，首席部長同議會由人民普選產生，有獨立經濟，有海水化淡同發電設施，水電都可以自給自足。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人睇完會唔會好羨慕？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAnyway, 支持蘋果，睇果籽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/G7IG1QflJgI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FG7IG1QflJgI&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5dDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=92af354f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/G7IG1QflJgI</a>"},{"pid":"3abe108bdb73f549ca3ce98de67707e5686c36f4","tid":2166360,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T11:22:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0277c949b9b143abe19e6ac1444f23532c5b64ee","tid":2166360,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T11:37:14.000Z","msg":"請推po<br />\n<br />\n【行動po求推】點解舊年824發生咁大件事都冇人記得？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2166297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2166297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LW7JmKm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src